<para style="q1">

<verse number="12" style="v" />For the sins of their mouths and the words of their lips,</para>

<para style="q1">let them be captured in their pride,</para>

<para style="q1">and for the curses and lies that they express.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="13" style="v" />Consume them in wrath, consume them so that they will be no more;</para>

<para style="q1">let them know that God rules in Jacob</para>

<para style="q1">and to the ends of the earth.

<char style="qs">Selah</char></para>
